title: Excuse Doesn't Live Here: You are Born to Win
description: Accept all your weaknesses, habits, pain and life scars as a part of your journey to becoming a better you. Life scars are the most beautiful handmade jeverly, make them shine with a pride. Don't ever let past control your, be in control. The sky is the limit, be the most beautiful star that universe created. Be you!!
author: Mirjana Barisic-Filipovic
